:<font size="15">ירק</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
ירק / yereq / yeh'-rek

===Etymology===
From {{HH|3417}} (in the sense of vacuity of color); 

===Noun===
'''ירק'''

# Properly [[pallor]], that is, hence the yellowish green of young and sickly vegetation; concretely verdure, that is, grass or vegetation: - [[grass]], [[green]] (thing).

